      "text": "\"Brain\" of the AI:\n- Localised Data which the agent stores\nencrypted on Ceramic/Hoku\n- This is the data the agent decides\nthat it has an asymmetrical advantage\nover other agents ingesting public data",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "6A8IyA3Tu3aSV1XHNY1FM",
      "originalText": "\"Brain\" of the AI:\n- Localised Data which the agent stores encrypted on Ceramic/Hoku\n- This is the data the agent decides that it has an asymmetrical advantage over other agents ingesting public data",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
